des:
With the LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi Skill you can control the SMART+ WiFi products with Alexa app or voice. More information soon.

After connecting Alexa to your LDV WiFi products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one account in our "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi" app;
(3). You need to have some devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi", and you'll be navigated to our login page;
(9). Input your LEDVANCE SMART+ WiFi account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
